    "- **Strategic sourcing decisions** requiring relationship management\n",
    "- **High-value supplier contracts** where human judgment is critical\n",
    "- **Complex procurement situations** with multiple competing factors\n",
    "- **Organizations building AI capabilities** with change management needs\n",
    "- **Regulated industries** requiring explainable decision processes"
